snippet.title: [Pokemon] / "Hey Amber, I remember your name" /
snippet.description:
EDIT: AUGH. I'm sorry the quality is so horrible! ;_;

NOTE: Yes, I know that the clips from the 'Birth of Mewtwo' are pretty terrible quality. I'll have a much better version in the next video that includes Mewtwo. 

 Recently heard Skillet's new album, and I just love this sad and beautiful song. And I was just in the mood for a Mewtwo/Amber tribute.
